<!-- Template: 教育风格-变体15 (Content #1655) - 现代文阅读·段落大意 -->
<div class="w-[1440px] h-[810px] relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #F8F7F4;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col">
        <!-- 顶部标题栏 -->
        <div class="h-[80px] flex items-center justify-between px-16" style="background-color: #2D3A8C;">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                <h1 class="text-[32px] font-bold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">现代文阅读技巧</h1>
                <div class="w-[1px] h-8" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"></div>
                <p class="text-[16px]" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">如何归纳段落大意</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[12px] tracking-[2px]" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">READING SKILLS</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 主内容区 -->
        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col px-16 py-8 gap-6">
            <!-- 示例段落 -->
            <div class="p-6" style="background-color: #EEF2F7;">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #2D3A8C;">
                        <span class="text-[16px]" style="color: #FFFFFF;">文</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-[20px] font-semibold" style="color: #1E293B;">示例段落</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
                    <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] indent-8" style="color: #374151;">春天来了，校园里的樱花树开满了粉色的花朵。清晨，阳光透过花瓣洒在地面上，形成斑驳的光影。同学们喜欢在樱花树下读书、聊天，享受这美好的时光。微风吹过，花瓣纷纷飘落，就像下了一场粉色的雪。老师说，樱花的花期很短，要珍惜眼前的美景。</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 三步法 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-5">
                <div class="p-5" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #2D3A8C;">
                            <span class="text-[14px] font-bold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold" style="color: #1E293B;">找主要人物</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-[16px]" style="color: #374151;">
                        <p>- 同学们</p>
                        <p>- 老师</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3 p-2" style="background-color: #EEF2F7;">
                        <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold" style="color: #2D3A8C;">提问：谁做了什么？</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="p-5" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #2D3A8C;">
                            <span class="text-[14px] font-bold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">2</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold" style="color: #1E293B;">找关键事物</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-[16px]" style="color: #374151;">
                        <p>- 樱花树</p>
                        <p>- 花瓣</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3 p-2" style="background-color: #EEF2F7;">
                        <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold" style="color: #2D3A8C;">提问：写了什么东西？</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="p-5" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #2D3A8C;">
                            <span class="text-[14px] font-bold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">3</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold" style="color: #1E293B;">找中心句</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2 text-[16px]" style="color: #374151;">
                        <p>- "春天来了..."</p>
                        <p>- "要珍惜美景"</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3 p-2" style="background-color: #EEF2F7;">
                        <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold" style="color: #2D3A8C;">提问：表达什么意思？</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 归纳结果 -->
            <div class="p-6" style="background-color: #1E293B;">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #E8573A;">
                        <span class="text-[16px]" style="color: #FFFFFF;">归</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-[20px] font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">段落大意归纳</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[16px] leading-relaxed" style="color: #CBD5E1;"><span class="font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">春天</span>校园里的<span class="font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">樱花盛开</span>，<span class="font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">同学们</span>在树下<span class="font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">欣赏美景</span>，老师提醒大家要<span class="font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">珍惜</span>短暂的<span class="font-semibold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">花期</span>。</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 归纳口诀 -->
            <div class="p-4 flex items-start gap-4" style="background-color: #FEF3E2; border-left: 4px solid #E8573A;">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #E8573A;">
                    <span class="text-[14px] font-bold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">!</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-[14px] font-semibold mb-1" style="color: #92400E;">归纳技巧口诀</p>
                    <p class="text-[16px]" style="color: #78350F;"><span class="font-bold">谁</span>(人物) + <span class="font-bold">在哪</span>(地点) + <span class="font-bold">做什么</span>(事件) + <span class="font-bold">怎么样</span>(结果/感受)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>